ges/offset-boxes.png" alt="Icon of two overlapping squares."> <h3>Streamlined Sales and Purchasing Process</h3> </li> </ul> </div> <div class="collage"> <img src="https://www.miva.com/images/new-images/right-3-2021.png" alt="Man with hardhat, talking on a smartphone and looking away with a clipboard."> </div> </div> <div id="secondSlide" class="slide clearfix"> <div class="contentFloat"> <p>Market, sell, and fulfill your products directly to customers with a fast and flexible ecommerce experience that streamlines processes and connects your brand with the world.</p> <a href="https://www.miva.com/dtc-ecommerce-platform" class="learn">Learn More <i class="icon-new-long-arrow"></i></a> <ul> <li> <img src="https://www.miva.com/images/new-images/offset-cart.png" alt="Icon of a shopping cart."> <h3>Outstanding Merchandising <br>and Promotions</h3> </li> <li> <img src="https://www.miva.com/images/new-images/offset-posse.png" alt="Icon of multiple human figures."> <h3>Brand-Centric <br>Shopping Experience</h3> </li> <li> <img src="https://www.miva.com/images/new-images/offset-glare.png" alt="Icon of a monitor with glare."> <h3>Manage All-In-One <br>Sales Channels</h3> </li> <li> <img src="https://www.miva.com/images/new-images/offset-handshake.png" alt="Icon of two hands shaking."> <h3>Top-Notch Partner <br>and Reseller Support</h3> </li> </ul> </div> <div class="collage"> <img src="https://www.miva.com/images/new-images/right-2-2021.png" alt="Man using a tablet and smiling."> </div> </div> <div id="thirdSlide" class="slide clearfix"> <div class="contentFloat"> <p>Everything you need to capture attention, showcase products, and create a masterful shopping experience from first click to fulfillment.</p> <a href="https://www.miva.com/b2c-ecommerce-platform" class="learn">Learn More <i class="icon-new-long-arrow"></i></a> <ul> <li> <img src="https://www.miva.com/images/new-images/offset-monitor-eye.png" alt="Icon of a monitor with an eye inside."> <h3>Dynamic Pages <br>and Promotions</h3> </li> <li> <img src="https://www.miva.com/images/new-images/offset-refresh.png" alt="Icon of a webpage with a refresh icon inside."> <h3>Conversion <br>Optimization</h3> </li> <li> <img src="https://www.miva.com/images/new-images/offset-write-doc.png" alt="Icon of a page with a pencil."> <h3>Stunning Product <br>Visualizers</h3> </li> <li> <img src="https://www.miva.com/images/new-images/offset-sale-tag.png" alt="Icon of a price tag."> <h3>Subscriptions and <br>Automated Reordering</h3> </li> </ul> </div> <div class="collage"> <img src="https://www.miva.com/images/new-images/right-1-2021.png" alt="Woman using a smarphone and smiling."> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="mivaRealizes" class="newWide clear clearfix"> <div class="wideContainer clearfix"> <div class="collage"> <div class="gradient1"></div> <img src="https://www.miva.com/images/new-images/rounded-teamwork-3.png" alt="Woman with glasses using a laptop in a group."> </div> <div class="contentFloat clearfix"> <h2>Bring us the problems other platforms can't handle.</h2> <div class="clearfix"> <p>Many Miva customers come to us when their complex product catalogs or specialized industry requirements have proved too challenging for other ecommerce platforms to manage. Over two decades of experience gives us the powerful expertise to excel at challenges that other platforms simply can't handle. Every customer wants an ecommerce solution that gives them more flexibility, more speed, and more control over every aspect of how they sell.</p> <p class="fauxH2">Legendary support</p> <p>At Miva, you're not just a number. Customers love our white glove support and total commitment to your success. We are proud to continuously develop solutions to modern merchants' most pressing needs, delivering first rate ecommerce for outstanding B2B and D2C businesses. We can't wait to help you discover your site's true potential.</p> <a href="https://www.miva.com/ecommerce-strategy-resource-guides" class